Day2

Css = cascding style sheets is the styling language used to add style to webpage

3 ways to add css to html
1.inline Css = added directly to html element
2.internal Css = defined at the head 
3.external Css = styles defined in separate file

extension = .css


css selectors (6) -> 
1.tag selectors 
2.class selectors
3.id selectors
4.universal selectors

syntax : 
selector{
    property : value;
}

Box model
div container used to divide web page in sections
block(div)and inline tag(span)
flexboard
grid